title: WinSnap v4.5.6 MultiLang Win All Incl.Generic Patch-SND
description:
NTWind WinSnap v4.5.6 MultiLang Win All





WinSnap is a screen capture utility that enables you to take
screenshots of non-rectangular windows and applications, using a
background of your choice as well as regular windows, the desktop,
popup menus and more. It can automatically enhance the capture with a
smooth drop shadow effect, add a watermark, change the coloring and
optionally save as a new file or copy it to the clipboard.
Other features include support for Aero effects, image rotation,
annotations, color effects advanced auto-saving, image scaling,
keyboard shortcuts and more. WinSnap can save your captures in PNG,
GIF, BMP, TIF and JPG format.



Support for Windows 10 (32- and 64-bit, Win10 Aero shadows, etc)
New translations: Dutch, French, Simplified Chinese, Ukrainian
Some other minor improvements and bug fixes


Installation:

. Unpack
. Install the application
. Patch the executable using our patcher
